public CommandParameters getParameters(CommandLine line)
Call to get the parameters from a commandline once a match has been found. This will attempt to turn all the parameters into the correct type. if the parameters fail to convert then an exception will be thrown.

getKey

public String getKey()
This is used to match against the first token in the command line. This is meant to be used to isolate those commands which start with same word like /loot or /info so that more powerful (and slower) match checks can take place.
